      <section eId="sec_625">
        <num>625</num>
        <heading>Assignment of contracts for services</heading>
        <subsection eId="sec_625__subsec_a">
          <num>(a)</num>
          <content>
            <p>the creditor is a person related to the seller of services; or\n</p>
          </content>
        </subsection>
        <subsection eId="sec_625__subsec_b">
          <num>(b)</num>
          <content>
            <p>the seller prepares documents used in connection with the loan; or\n</p>
          </content>
        </subsection>
        <subsection eId="sec_625__subsec_c">
          <num>(c)</num>
          <content>
            <p>the creditor supplies forms to the seller used by the consumer in\nobtaining the loan; or\n</p>
          </content>
        </subsection>
        <subsection eId="sec_625__subsec_d">
          <num>(d)</num>
          <content>
            <p>the creditor makes twenty or more loans in any calendar year, the\nproceeds of which are used in transactions with the same seller or with\na person related to the same seller; or\n</p>
          </content>
        </subsection>
        <subsection eId="sec_625__subsec_e">
          <num>(e)</num>
          <content>
            <p>the consumer is referred to the creditor by the seller; or\n</p>
          </content>
        </subsection>
        <subsection eId="sec_625__subsec_f">
          <num>(f)</num>
          <content>
            <p>the creditor, directly or indirectly, pays the seller any\nconsideration whether or not it is in connection with the particular\ntransactions; or\n</p>
          </content>
        </subsection>
        <subsection eId="sec_625__subsec_g">
          <num>(g)</num>
          <content>
            <p>the creditor participated in or was connected with the sale.\n  3. No assignee of a contract shall fail to give notice of the\nassignment to the consumer. A notice of assignment shall be in writing\naddressed to the consumer at the address shown on the contract and shall\nidentify the contract.\n</p>
          </content>
        </subsection>
      </section>
